• Support research and study activities on relevant climate change topics that will benefit the further development and innovation of the joint project activities as well as that of the long-term development of the VN-SIPA project;
• Facilitate the communication and cooperation between DCC, MAE and GIZ with regard to the implementation of the German ODA-funded technical cooperation projects;
• Ensure and maintain close and effective cooperation among PIT members, cooperation between PIT and project implementation team, as well as cooperation with international/ national experts and project partners;
• Represent the project in various fora as requested.

